<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink123">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kaṇṭiku mallamō koṇkaniṉ kēḷē</l>
<l>yoṇṇuta lāya mārppat</l>
<l>taṇṇeṉ peruṅkaṭaṟ ṟiraipāy vōḷē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>We have seen your friend, haven't we, oh man from the sea?</l>
<l>She who leapt into the waves of the cool, great ocean,</l>
<l>As her group [of ladies] with bright foreheads called out?</l>
</lg>
    </div>
